<section>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12 m4">
      <h5>What is this Bagel Radio?</h5>
      <p>
        <a href="http://somafm.com/bagel/" target="_blank">Bagel Radio</a> is a station on <a href="http://somafm.com" target="_blank">Soma FM</a> playing a mix of old school and cutting edge alternative music. <a href="https://twitter.com/bagel_somafm?lang=en" target="_blank">Music director Ted</a> hosts two live shows each week while listeners gather <a href="https://internet-radio-slack.herokuapp.com" target="_blank">on Slack</a> to discuss the latest musical shenanigans.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12 m4">
      <h5>What is this site?</h5>
      <p>
        Listeners of <a href="http://somafm.com/bagel/ " target="_blank">Bagel Radio</a> tend to be huge fans of sometimes obscure bands. In many cases, it's very easy to miss Bagel bands coming through your town. This tool lets you know when bands are coming to your area!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <h5>How do I use this site?</h5>
        <p>Simply enter some geographical data (city and state, zip code, etc) and the distance you're willing to travel, and we'll provide a concert listing worthy of a serious music nerd.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="divider"></div>
  <section>
    <div class="row">
      <%= form_for @conn, Routes.page_path(@conn, :process_search), [name: :search], fn f -> %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="input-field col s12 m6">
          <%= text_input f, :search_term, [required: ""] %>
          <label for="first_name">Location</label>
        </div>
        <div class="input-field col s6 m3">
          <%= select f, :range, [10, 25, 50, 75, 100, 250] %>
          <label>Select Distance in Miles</label>
        </div>
        <div class="input-field col s6 m3">
          <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">Submit
            <i class="fas fa-caret-square-right"></i>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="row">
    <%= if (@conn.request_path == "/process_search") do %>
    <%= if length(@events) == 0 do %>
    <h5>Sorry, there were no results for your area.</h5>
    <% end %>
    <ul class="collapsible" >
      <%= for event <- @events do %>
      <li>
        <div class="collapsible-header">
          <a href="<%= event.url%>" target="_blank">
            <%= Enum.join [event.datetime.year, event.datetime.month, event.datetime.day], "/" %>
          </a>
           - <a href="<%= event.artist.url %>" target="_blank"><%= event.artist.name %></a>
           - <%= event.venue.name %>
           - <%= event.venue.city %>, <%= event.venue.region %>
        </div>
        <div class="collapsible-body">
        <div>
            <h6>Description</h6>
            <span><%= event.description %></span>
            <h6>Lineup</h6>
            <ul>
              <%= for band <- event.lineup do %>
              <li><%= band %></li>
              <% end %>
            </ul>
          </div>
          </div>
      </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
    <% end %>
  </div>

        <footer class="page-footer">
        <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col l6 s12">
                        <h5 class="white-text">Technology Enlisted</h5>
                        <p class="grey-text text-lighten-4">This site was built using the following technologies</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col l4 offset-l2 s12">
                        <h5 class="white-text">Links</h5>
                        <ul>
                          <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="https://www.bandsintown.com" target="_blank">Bands in Town</a></li>
                          <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="https://phoenixframework.org"target="_blank">Phoenix Web Framework</a></li>
                          <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="https://elixir-lang.org"target="_blank">Elixir Programming Language</a></li>
                          <li><a class="grey-text text-lighten-3" href="http://www.wolfram.com/mathematica/?source=nav"target="_blank">Mathematica/Wolfram Langauge</a></li>
                        </ul>
                      </div>
                      </div>
                      </div>
          <div class="footer-copyright">
            <div class="container">
            Â© 2019 Bagel Concert Finder
            <%= for stat <- @stats do %>
            <span class="grey-text text-lighten-4 right" href="#!"> <%= stat.name %>: <%= stat.value %>&nbsp;</span>
            <%= end %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </footer>